{"tid":1974373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關大帽山棄屍案猜想","createTime":"2020-04-15T20:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T06:35:17.000Z","uid":26770,"like":19,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fc41ff8f677771599a8855a1cea85136fe11009e","tid":1974373,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:01:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200415/5XX6FLTTRTTES7VXHED74IWH3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200415%2F5XX6FLTTRTTES7VXHED74IWH3U%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=e15ba9bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200415%2F5XX6FLTTRTTES7VXHED74IWH3U%2F&h=4be6c38e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200415/5XX6FLTTRTTES7VXHED74IWH3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n1 當係行山跌親撞暈左死埋係解唔通點解用綿被卷自己<br />\n一定係殺人棄屍<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n[獨居翁疑病發猝逝半年房署爆門驚見白骨<br />\n青衣長宏邨獨居翁，疑在住所內猝死無人知，房署人員發現他多個月未交租，查看無果，昨午決定上門爆門入屋，揭發租客已變白骨，]<br />\n<br />\n大帽山濕度高,溫度高,大風會更快變白骨<br />\n我當五個月<br />\n香港警魔係831開始大量殺人, 打頭壓頸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">起因係8月頭已遭放料係新屋嶺輪姦大量少女,打到大量示威者重傷,香港警魔想把香港變警察國家避過坐監<br />\n</span><br />\n呢位死者的死亡日期絕對於香港警魔開始大量殺人後<br />\n<br />\n3 <br />\n大帽山有部分路係車路<br />\n係車路落車抄小路棄屍係最可能的方案<br />\n<br />\n香港警魔有隊人叫Rural Patrol Team RPT<br />\n鄉村巡邏隊, 坊間稱穿山甲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係行開山又有車又殺開人</span>"},{"pid":"0e6a150495c24d34f2e6cb69c148c3f4bcd0dd40","tid":1974373,"uid":8014,"like":21,"dislike":14,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:09:37.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑驚又殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你都係想我覆呢d 姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221ac7d6e4c31a2b8c0678330fa6e3027b055a58","tid":1974373,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:11:10.000Z","msg":"立即比五毛招呼,仲唔係講中香港警魔"},{"pid":"9f7dd603730d9918fc80468af2838db989ad4f73","tid":1974373,"uid":8014,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"221ac7d6e4c31a2b8c0678330fa6e3027b055a58","tid":1974373,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:11:10.000Z","msg":"立即比五毛招呼,仲唔係講中香港警魔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:13:31.000Z","msg":"係嘅大偵探<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcaa6dfd0dc082fd8b77a59b6bbcd92f9b24c80c","tid":1974373,"uid":67089,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:39:40.000Z","msg":"仲偉大過黎曼猜想，幾時攞土地奬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58153dd9110ac714bb67ecec5d053f36a74bb959","tid":1974373,"uid":7270,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:42:45.000Z","msg":"仲有一點<br />\n有咩人殺人唔會比人捉到？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就係警渣呀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f4c7c07127a126724201d6b79028f77b911869f8","tid":1974373,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:43:28.000Z","msg":"大約5x歲喎"},{"pid":"01ad08ce47565a8e46b0e30a7f6af6d16765d96b","tid":1974373,"uid":141625,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:45:36.000Z","msg":"唔好係零基礎嘅情況下上崗上線<br />\n咁樣做得多 以後有真憑實據嘅時候就冇人會信<br />\n黑警係仆街 但事實係未必乜都關黑警事"},{"pid":"af1600a155ae62af78c9b9d0f60c774e6395f9be","tid":1974373,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:49:38.000Z","msg":"濕氣重既位要去到山道停車場先會重"},{"pid":"0cd557359ee0251f312140f2587d37f9394956b6","tid":1974373,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58153dd9110ac714bb67ecec5d053f36a74bb959","tid":1974373,"uid":7270,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T20:42:45.000Z","msg":"仲有一點<br />\n有咩人殺人唔會比人捉到？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><str